ngerous areas - known as the \"Wall\" - are filled with mystery and danger. As the deadline looms, you will have to quickly overcome traps, puzzles, and dancing minigames to make it through in time.  Luckily, you have your confidants by your side to help when things get scary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Animated Cutscenes</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/a1d2d1092742ab743127435877d00809.poster.avif?t=1759232313\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/a1d2d1092742ab743127435877d00809.webm?t=1759232313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402110/extras/a1d2d1092742ab743127435877d00809.mp4?t=1759232313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are several fully 2D animated cutscenes that change depending on who you decide to date. Immerse yourself and truly connect with the characters you are spending time with.",
